lass of Lie algebras $\\mathfrak g $ that\nare defined by partial orders, $m_\\mathrm{faithful}(\\mathcal G_R)$ is given by\na single polynomial-type formula.\n  Finally, we compute $m_\\mathrm{faithful}(\\mathcal G_R)$ precisely in the case\nwhere $\\mathfrak g$ is the free metabelian nilpotent Lie algebra of class $c$\non $n$ generators and $R$ is a finite truncated valuation ring.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 16:13:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-27"}
