 to mixing with\nthe star, resulting in jets with a hybrid composition of magnetic and thermal\ncomponents at the photosphere, where $\\sim 10\\%$ of the gas maintains\nmagnetization $\\sigma\\gtrsim 0.1$. This indicates that both a photospheric\ncomponent and reconnection may play a role in the prompt emission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 18:00:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 1 Jun 2022 15:34:47 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Jun 2022 02:07:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-06"}
