ed shapes once we include baryons in the\nsimulations. Our results demonstrate that this is essential to derive realistic\nconstraints and that new simulations are needed to confirm and extend our\nfindings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Apr 2022 18:00:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Sep 2022 13:05:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-14"}
