nary\ncomponent (more luminous) we also computed the flux density ratio of the\nsystems by utilizing the area of the eclipses. In addition, the positions of\nthe systems in the H-R diagram were examined considering the flux density\nratios. As a consequence of the investigation, we defined 38 candidates Delta\nScuti and also one Maia variable in eclipsing binary systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 27 Apr 2022 14:04:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
